c: 2
v: 27
t: "Avo vanotyora chirangano (chitsidzo) chaAllah mushure yewirirano yacho, uye vanotyora izvo zvavakakomekedzwa naAllah kuti vabatanidze (Chitendero chaAllah, nokutevedzera mitemo yacho pano pasi uye kuchengetedza hukama), uye nokuita zvisakarurama panyika. Vanhu vanodaro ndivo vakarasikirwa"